The paper deals with the analysis of weight matrices of Deep Neural Networks (DNNs) and their training process. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.IT (Information Theory) as they are also related to the study of neural networks. The paper also discusses the statistical physics of disordered systems, which falls under cs.SI (Systems and Control) and cs.SY (Control and Systems Engineering).
